    "description": "ACTUS DeFi ETH Portfolio: OPTION B - BUFFER-FIRST with PP STATE CORRECTION (90-DAY TEST)\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nOPTION B: SOPHISTICATED BUFFER-FIRST STRATEGY + PP STATE CORRECTION\n  ✅ Sells from 4.0 ETH BUFFER (not collateral)\n  ✅ Preserves 3.0 ETH collateral quantity CONSTANT\n  ✅ LTV always calculated using original 3.0 ETH\n  ✅ Circuit breaker: max 3 interventions, min 1.0 ETH reserve\n  ✅ Falling knife detection: stops if price drops >20% in 48hr\n  ✅ 24-hour cooldown between interventions\n  ✅ NEW: PP state correction enabled - shows reduced loan balance!\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nNEW IN V4:\n  The PAM contract now has `enablePPStateCorrection: true` attribute.\n  This triggers post-processing in actus-service webapp layer to correct\n  the nominalValue field in PP events, showing the loan balance AFTER\n  prepayment instead of BEFORE.\n\nSIMULATION PERIOD: 90 DAYS (faster testing)\n  Start: 2026-02-18\n  End: 2026-05-19\n  Maturity: 2126-02-18 (100-year perpetual)\n\nPORTFOLIO:\n  Total ETH: 7.0 ETH\n    - Collateral: 3.0 ETH (NEVER CHANGES)\n    - Buffer: 4.0 ETH (defense fund)\n\nScenario: ETH $2800 → $1870 (-33%), Rate 5.0% → 11.5%\n\nFIXED CALCULATION: Correct loan balance tracking with interest accrual",
